    {
      "id": "18f4750c-f3ba-8034-a03c-cf0e9b7274ea",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Efficient groups are pivotal towards success in collaborative learning settings. The authors use Belbin typology (which has 9 possible roles in groups) to propose a Fuzzy-based Multi-Agent Model fgor group formation. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "18f4750c-f3ba-8034-a03c-cf0e9b7274ea",
        "parent": {
