    {
      "id": "18f4750c-f3ba-8060-9064-ce77bb086acc",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The authors use a fuzzy logic to classify role performance inside the group. Authors create a prototype and test the effectiveness of their approach via a case study.",
